hadiths[105]{hadithnumber,text}:
5678,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Allah Taala ne koi aisi bimari nahi utari jiski dawaa bhi nazil na ki ho.
5679,"ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath ghazawaat mein Sharik hoti thin aur musalman Mujahid ko pani pilaatii , unki khidmat kartin aur qatl honey walon aur zakhmiyon ko Madina Munawra laya kartii thin."
5680,"shifa teen chizon mein hai. shehad ke sharbat mein, pachhna lagwaaney main aur aag se daaghney mein lekin main ummat ko aag se dagh kar ilaaj karne se mana karta hun. Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne is hadis ko marfooan naql kya hai aur al-qamii ne riwayat kya, unse Leis ne, unse Mujahid ne, unse Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne aur unse Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne shehad aur pachhna lagwaaney ke barey mein bayan kya."
5681,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke shifa teen chizon mein hai pachhna lagwaaney mein, shehad peeney main aur aag se daaghney mein magar main apni ummat ko aag se daaghney se mana karta hun."
5682,"mujhey Hisham ne khabar di, unhein unke walid ne aur unse Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko meethaa aur shehad pasand tha."
5683,"maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke agar tumhari dawaaon mein kisi mein bhalai hai ya ye kaha ke tumhari (in) dawaaon mein bhalai hai. to pachhna lagwaaney ya shehad peeney aur aag se daaghney mein hai agar wo marz ke mutabiq ho aur main aag se daaghney ko pasand nahi karta hun."
5684,"aik sahib Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur arz kya ke mera bhai pet ki takleef mein mubtala hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke unhein shehad pilaa, phir dusri martaba wahi sahabi hazir huey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey us martaba bhi shehad pilaaney ke liye kaha wo phir teesri martaba aaya aur arz kya ke) hukm ke mutabiq ( maine amal kya ( lekin shifa nahi huii). Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Allah Taala sachcha hai aur tumharey bhai ka pet jhoota hai, unhein phir shehad pilaa. chunanche unhon-ne shehad phir pilaya aur usi se wo tandurust ho gaya."
5685,"kuchh logon ko bimari thi, unhon-ne kaha : ya Rasulullah ! hamein qiyam ki jagah inayat farma dein aur hamarey khaney ka intizam kar dein phir jab wo log tandurust ho gaey to unhon-ne kaha ke Madina ki aab w hawa kharaab hai chunanche Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne maqam Harra mein oonton ke sath unke qiyam ka intizam kar diya aur farmaya ke unka doodh piyo jab wo tandurust ho gaey to unhon-ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke charwaahey ko qatl kar diya aur oonton ko haank kar ley gaey. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unke peechhey aadmi daudaaey aur wo pakdey gaey (jaisaa ke unhon-ne charwaahey ke sath kya tha) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bhi waisaa hi kya unke haath-paaun katwaa diye aur unki aankhon mein salaaii phirwaa di. maine unmein se aik shakhs ko dekha ke zaban se zameen chaatta tha aur usi haalat mein wo mar gaya. salam ne bayan kya ke mujhey malum hua ke Hajjaj ne Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha tum mujh se wo sabse sakht saza bayan karo jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kisi ko di ho to unhon-ne yahi waqia bayan kya jab imam Hasan Basri tak ye baat pahunchi to unhon-ne kaha kash! wo ye hadis Hajjaj se na bayan kartey."
5686,( Uraina ke) kuchh logon ko Madina Munawra ki aab w hua muwafiq nahi aai thi to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse farmaya ke wo aap (Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam)) ke charwaahey ke yahan chaley jayen yani oonton main aur unka doodh aur peshab piein. chunanche wo log Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke charwaahey ke paas chaley gaey aur oonton ka doodh aur peshab piyaa jab wo tandurust ho gaey to unhon-ne charwaahey ko qatl kar diya aur oonton ko haank kar ley gaey. aapko jab iska ilm hua to aap ne unhein talash karne ke liye logon ko bheja jab unhein laya gaya to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke hukm se unke bhi hath aur paon kaat diye gaey aur unki aankhon mein salaaii pher di gaee ( jaisa ke unhon-ne charwaahey ke sath kya tha) . Qatada ne bayan kya ke mujh se Muhammad-bin Sirin ne bayan kya ke ye hudood ke nazil honey se pahley ka waqia hai.
5687,"ham bahar gaey huey they aur hamarey sath ghalib bin-Abjar (Raziallahu anhu) bhi they. wo rasta mein bimar pad gaey phir jab ham Madina wapas aaey us waqt bhi wo bimar hi they. ibne-abi-Atiq unki iyaadat ke liye tashrif laey aur ham se kaha ke unhein ye kaley daney (kalonjii) istemal karaao, iske panch ya saat (7) daney lekar pees lo aur phir Zaitoon ke tel mein mila kar (naak ke) us taraf aur us taraf usey qatra qatra karke tapkaao. kyonke Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne mujh se bayan kya ke unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ye kalonjii har bimari ki dawaa hai siwa ( saam ( ke. maine arz kya ( saam ( kya hai? farmaya ke maut hai."
5688,"mujhey abu-Salma aur Saeed-bin-Musaiyab ne khabar di aur unhein Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne khabar di, unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke siyah daanon mein har bimari se shifa hai siwa ( saam ( ke. ibne-Shahab ne kaha ke) saam ( maut hai aur siyah daana kalonjii ko kehtey hain."
5689,"Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bimar ke liye aur maiyat ke sogwaaron ke liye talbeena ( munasib , doodh aur shehad mila kar daliya ( pakaaney ka hukm deti thin aur farmati thin ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke talbeena mareez ke dil ko sukoon pahunchata hai aur gham ko door karta hai (kyonke usey peeney ke baad umuman neend aa jati hai ye Hazam karnewaalaa bhi hai)."
5690,wo talbeena pakaaney ka hukm deti thin aur farmati thin ke agarche wo ( mareez ko) na-pasand hota hai lekin wo usko fayda deta hai.
5691,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne pachhna lagwaayaa aur pachhna lagaaney waley ko uski mazdoorii di aur naak mein dawaa dalwaaii .
5692,"maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tum log is aud hindii ( كست (ka istemal kya karo kyonke usmein saat (7) beemaariyon ka ilaaj hai. halaq ke dard mein usey naak mein daala jata hai, paslii ke dard mein chabaaii jati hai."
5693,aur main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat main apne aik doodh-peetey ladkey ko lekar hazir hui phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke uper us ne peshab kar diya to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne pani mangwa kar peshab ki jagah par chhinta diya.
5694,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (eik martaba ( roze ki haalat mein pachhna lagwaayaa .
5695,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne pachhna lagwaayaa jabke aap ehram se they.
5696,unse pachhna lagwaaney waley ki mazdoorii ke barey mein puchha gaya tha. unhon-ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne pachhna lagwaayaa tha aapko abu-Taiba ( Naafe ya Maisra ( ne pachhna lagaya tha Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein do saa khajoor mazdoorii mein di thi aur aap ne unke maalikon ( banu- Harisa ( se guftgu ki to unhon-ne unse wsool kiye janey waley lagaan mein kami kar di thi aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke (khoon ke dabaaw ka ( behtreen ilaaj jo tum kartey ho wo pachhna lagwaanaa hai aur umda dawaa aud hindii ka istemal karna hai aur farmaya apne bachchon ko) عذرة ( (halaq ki beemaarii) mein unka taaloo daba kar takleef mat do balke (kust) laga do us se waram jata rahega.
5697,"Jabir-bin-Abdullah miqna-bin-Sanaan Taabai ki iyaadat ke liye tashrif laey phir unse kaha ke jab tak tum pachhna na lagwaa logey mein yahan se nahi jaunga, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna hai ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke usmein shifa hai."
5698,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Makka ke rastey mein maqam Luhiy-jamal main apne sar ke beech mein pachhna lagwaayaa Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us waqt ehram ki haalat mein they.
5699,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne sar mein pachhna lagwaayaa.
5700,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne haalate-ehraam main apne sar mein pachhna lagwaayaa (ye pachhna aap ne sar ke) dard ki wjah se lagwaayaa tha jo Luhyi-jamal naam ke pani ke ghaat par aapko ho gaya tha.
5701,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ehram ki haalat main apne sar mein pachhna lagwaayaa . aadhey sar ke dard ki wjah se jo aapko ho gaya tha.
5702,"maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke agar tumhari dawaaiyon mein koi bhalai hai to shehad ke sharbat mein hai aur pachhna lagwaaney mein hai aur aag se daaghney mein hai lekin main aag se dagh kar ilaaj ko pasand nahi karta."
5703,suleh Hudaibiya ke mauqe par Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mere paas tashrif laey mein aik handi ke nichey aag jalaa raha tha aur juwein mere sar se gir rahi thi (aur mein ehram baandhey huey tha) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya ke sar ki ye juwein tumhen takleef pahunchaatii hain? maine arz kya ke ji haan. farmaya ke phir sar mundwaa ley aur (kaffaare ke taur par) teen din ke rozey rakh ya chh miskinon ko khana khilaa ya aik qurbani kar de. Ayub ne kaha ke mujhey yad nahi ke (un teen chizon mein se) kis ka zikr sabse pahley kya tha.
5704,"maine Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, unse Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke agar tumhari dawaaon mein shifa hai to pachhna lagwaaney aur aag se daaghney mein hai lekin aag se dagh kar ilaaj ko main pasand nahi karta."
5705,"nazare-bd aur zahreeley janwar ke kaat khaney ke siwa aur kisi cheez par jhaad phoonk sahi nahi. (haseen ne bayan kya ke) phir maine iska zikr Saeed-bin-Jubair se kya to unhon-ne bayan kya ke ham se Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke mere samney tamam ummatein pesh ki gain eik-eik, 2-2 Nabi aur unke sath unke manney waley guzartey rahe aur kuchh Nabi aisey bhi they ke unke sath koi nahi tha aakhir mere samney aik badi bhari jamat aai. maine puchha ye kon hain, kya ye meri ummat ke log hain? kaha gaya ke ye Musa (Alaihissalam) aur unki qaum hai phir kaha gaya ke kinaron ki taraf dekho maine dekha ke aik bahut hi azeem jamat hai jo kinaron par chhaaii hui hai phir mujh se kaha gaya ke idhar dekho, idhar dekho aasman ke mukhtalif kinaron mein maine dekha ke jamat hai jo tamam ufuq par chhaaii hui hai. kaha gaya ke ye aap ki ummat hai aur is mein se 70 hazaar hisab ke baghair jannat mein dakhil kar diye jaengey. iske baad aap (apne hujre mein) tashrif le gaey aur kuchh tafseel nahi farmai log un jannatiyon ke barey mein bahas karne lagey aur kehney lagey ke ham Allah par eman laey hain aur uske rasool ki ittaba (pairvi) ki hai, isliye ham hi (sahaaba) wo log hain ya hamari wo aulad hain jo Islam mein paida huey kyonke ham jahiliyat mein paida huey they. ye baatein jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko malum huin to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bahar tashrif laey aur farmaya ke ye wo log hongey jo jhaad-phoonk nahi karaatey, faal nahi dekhtey aur dagh kar ilaaj nahi kartey balke apne rab par bharosa kartey hain. is par Ukaasha-bin-Mohsin (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah! kya main bhi unmein se hun. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke haan. iske baad doosrey sahabi khadey huey aur arz kya : ya Rasulullah! main bhi unmein hoon? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Ukasha tum se bazi ley gaey."
5706,aik aurat ke shauhar ka intiqal ho gaya (iddat key zamaane mein) us aurat ki aankh dukhney lagi to logon ne iska zikr Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kya. un logon ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney surme ka zikr kya aur ye ke (agar surma aankh mein na lagaya to ( unki aankh ke mutaalliq khatrah hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke) zamana jahiliyat mein) iddat guzarney wali tum aurton ke apne ghar mein sabse badtar kapdey mein padaa rehna padta tha ya (aap ne ye farmaya ke) apne kapdon mein ghar ke sabse badtar hisse mein padaa rehna padta tha phir jab koi kutta guzarta to is par wo mengni phenk kar maartii ( tab iddat se bahar hoti ( to char mahiney das din tak surma na lagaao .
5707,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke chhoot lagna, badshigoonii lenaa, ulloo ka manhoos hona aur safar ka manhoos hona ye sab bekaar khayalat hain albatta juzaamii shakhs se aisey bhaagta reh jaisey ke sher se bhaagta hai."
5708,"maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke khumbii ( من ( mein se hai aur iska pani aankh ke liye shifa hai. isi sanad se Shoba ne bayan kya ke mujhey Hakam-bin-Utaibaa ne khabar di, unhein Hasan-bin- Abdullah arnii ne, unhein Amr-bin-Hurais ne aur unhein Saeed-bin-Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) ne aur unhein Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne yahi hadis bayan ki, Shoba ne kaha ke jab Hakam ne bhi mujh se ye hadis bayan kar di to phir abdul-Malik-bin-Umair ki riwayat par mujh ko aitimad ho gaya kyonke Abdul-Malik ka haafiza aakhir mein bigad gaya tha Shoba ko sirf uski riwayat par bharosa na raha."
5709,Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki laash Mubarak ko bosa diya.
5710,Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki laash Mubarak ko bosa diya.
5711,Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki laash Mubarak ko bosa diya.
5712,"Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha ham ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke marz ( wafat ( mein dawaa aap ke munh mein dali to aap ne hamein ishara kya ke dawaa munh mein na dalo ham ne khayal kya ke mareez ko dawaa se jo nafrat hoti hai uski wjah se Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mana farma rahe hain phir jab aapko hosh hua to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke kyon maine tumhen mana nahi kya tha ke dawaa mere munh mein na daalo. ham ne arz kya ke ye shayad aap ne mareez ki dawaa se tabae nafrat ki wjah se farmaya hoga. is par Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ab ghar mein jitney log is waqt maujood hain sab ke munh mein dawaa dali jaey aur main dekhta rahoonga, albatta Abbas ko chhod diya jaey kyonke wo mere munh mein daltey waqt maujood na they, baad mein aaey."
5713,"main apne aik ladkey ko lekar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hui. maine uski naak mein battii dali thi, iska halaq dabaayaa tha chunkey usko galey ki bimari ho gaee thi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tum apne bachchon ko ungli se halaq daba kar kyon takleef deti ho ye aud hindii lo ismein saat (7) beemaariyon ki shifa hai unmein aik zaatul-janb (paslii ka waram bhi hai) agar halaq ki bimari ho to usko naak mein dalo agar zaatul-janb ho to halaq mein daalo. Sufiyan kehtey hain ke maine Zohri se suna, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne 2 beemaariyon ko to bayan kya baqi panch beemaariyon ko bayan nahi farmaya, Ali-bin-Abdullaah madeenii ne kaha maine Sufiyan se kaha, Mamar to Zohri se yun naql karta hai) أعلقت عنه ( unhon-ne kaha ke Mamar ne yad nahi rakha. mujhey yad hai Zohri ne yun kaha tha ( أعلقت عليه‏) aur Sufiyan ne us tehneek ko bayan kya, jo bachche ko paidaaish ke waqt ki jati hai. Sufiyan ne ungli halaq mein daal kar apne koey ko ungli se uthaya to Sufiyan ne ( أعلاق (ka mana bachchey ke halaq mein ungli daal kar taaloo ko uthaya unhon-ne ye nahi kaha ( أعلقوا عنه شيئا‏)."
5714,"mujh ko Ubaidullah-bin-Abdullaah-bin-Utba ne khabar di aur unse Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki paak bevi Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke jab (marzul-maut mein) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye chalnaa phirnaa dushwar ho gaya aur aap ki takleef badh gaee to aap ne bimari ke din mere ghar mein guzarney ki ijazat apni dusri beeviyon se maangii. jab ijazat mil gaee to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) 2 logon, Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) aur aik sahib ke darmyan unka sahara lekar bahar tashrif laaey, aap ke Mubarak qadam zameen par ghisat rahe they. maine Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se iska zikr kya to unhon-ne kaha tumhen malum hai wo doosrey sahib kon they jinka Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne naam nahi bataya, maine kaha ke nahi kaha ke wo Ali (Raziallahu anhu) they. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha ke unke hujrey mein dakhil honey ke baad Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya jabke aap ka marz badh gaya tha ke mujh par saat (7) mashk dalo jo pani se labrez hun. shayad mein logon ko kuchh nasihat kar sakun . bayan kya ke phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ham ne aik lagan mein bithaya jo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki paak bevi Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ka tha aur aap par hukm ke mutabiq mashkon se pani dalney lagey aakhir aap ne hamein ishara kya ke bas ho chukaa. bayan kya ke phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sahaba ke majme' mein gaey, unhein Namaz padhai aur unhein Khattab farmaayaa."
5715,"umme-Qais binte- Mohsin Asadiya ne unhein khabar di, unka talluq qabila Khuzaima ki shaakh-bin-Asad se tha wo un shuruati muhaajaraat mein se thin jinhoney Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bait ki thi. aap Ukaasha-bin-Mohsin (Raziallahu anhu) ki behan hain (unhon-ne bayan kya ke) wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat main apne aik betey ko lekar aaein. unhon-ne apne ladkey ke) عذرة (ka ilaaj taaloo daba kar kya tha Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, aakhir tum auratein kyon apni aulad ko yun taaloo daba kar takleef pahunchaatii ho. tumhen chahiye ke us marz mein aud hindii ka istemal kya karo kyonke usmein saat (7) beemaariyon se shifa hai. unmein aik zaatul-janb ki bimari bhi hai. (aud hindii se) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki murad ( كست ( thi yahi aud hindii hai. aur Yunus aur Ishaq bin Rashid ne bayan kya aur unse Zohri ne is riwayat mein bajaey ( اعلقت عليه‏ . Mina ( ke) علقت عليه‏ . Mina ( naql kya hai."
5716,aik sahib Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur arz kya ke mere bhai ko dast aa rahe hain Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke unhein shehad pulaaw. unhon-ne pilaya aur phir wapas aa kar kaha ke maine unhein shehad pilaya lekin unke daston mein koi kami nahi hui. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is par farmaya ke Allah Taala ne sach farmaya aur tumharey bhai ka pet jhoota hai (aakhir shehad hi se usey shifa hui) Muhammad-bin-Jafar ke sath us hadis ko Nazar-bin-Shumail ne bhi Shoba se riwayat kya hai.
5717,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, beemaariyon mein chhoot-chhaat safar aur ulloo ki nahoosat ki koi asl nahi is par aik dehati bola ke ya Rasulullah! phir mere oonton ko kya ho gaya ke wo jab tak registaan mein rahtey hain to hirnon ki tarah (saaf aur khub chikney) rahtey hain phir unmein aik khaarish wala oont aa jata hai aur unmein ghus kar unhein bhi khaarish laga jata hai to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is par farmaya lekin ye bataao ke pahley oont ko kis ne khaarish lagai thi? uski riwayat Zohri ne abu-Salma aur Sanan bin Sanan ke waaste se ki hai."
5718,"Umme- Qais binte- Mohsin jo pahley pahal hijrat karne wali aurton mein se thin jinhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bait ki thi aur wo ukaasha-bin-mohsin (Raziallahu anhu) ki behan thin, khabar di ke wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat main apne betey ko lekar hazir huin. unhon-ne us bachchey ka kowa girney mein taaloo daba kar ilaaj kya tha. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Allah se daro ke tum apni aulad ko is tarah taaloo daba kar takleef pahunchaatii ho aud hindii (koot) usmein istemal karo kyonke usmein saat (7) beemaariyon ke liye shifa hai jin mein se aik nimooniya bhi hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki murad aud hindii se ( كست ( thi jisey ( qist ( bhi kehtey hain ye bhi aik lughat hai."
5719,"Ayub sakhtiyan ke samney abu-Qilaba ki likhi hui hadison padhi gain unmein wo hadison bhi thin jinhein ( Ayub ne abu-Qilaba se) bayan kya tha aur wo bhi thin jo unke samney padh kar sunai gaee thin. un likhi hui hadison ke zakheere mein Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ki ye hadis bhi thi ke abu-Talha aur Anas-bin-Nazar ne Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ko dagh laga kar unka ilaaj kya tha ya abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ne unko khud apne hath se daaghaa tha aur Ibaad-bin-Mansoor ne bayan kya, unse Ayub ne, unse abu-Qilaba ne aur unse Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne qabila Ansar ke kuchh gharaanon ko zahreeley janwaron ke kaatney aur kaan ki takleef mein jhadney ki ijazat di thi to Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke zaatul-janb ki bimari mein mujhey daaghaa gaya tha Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki zindagi main aur us waqt abu-Talha, Anas-bin-Nazar aur Zaid-bin-Saabit (Raziallahu anhu) maujood they aur abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ne mujhey daaghaa tha."
5720,"Ayyoob sakhtiyan ke samney abu-Qilaba ki likhi hui hadison padhi gain unmein wo hadison bhi thin jinhein ( Ayub ne abu-Qilaba se) bayan kya tha aur wo bhi thin jo unke samney padh kar sunai gaee thin. un likhi hui hadison ke zakheere mein Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ki ye hadis bhi thi ke abu-Talha aur Anas-bin-Nazar ne Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ko dagh laga kar unka ilaaj kya tha ya abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ne unko khud apne hath se daaghaa tha aur Ibaad-bin-Mansoor ne bayan kya, unse Ayub ne, unse abu-Qilaba ne aur unse Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne qabila Ansar ke kuchh gharaanon ko zahreeley janwaron ke kaatney aur kaan ki takleef mein jhadney ki ijazat di thi to Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke zaatul-janb ki bimari mein mujhey daaghaa gaya tha Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki zindagi main aur us waqt abu-Talha, Anas-bin-Nazar aur Zaid-bin-Saabit (Raziallahu anhu) maujood they aur abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ne mujhey daaghaa thaa."
5721,"Ayyoob sakhtiyan ke samney abu-Qilaba ki likhi hui hadison padhi gain unmein wo hadison bhi thin jinhein ( Ayub ne abu-Qilaba se) bayan kya tha aur wo bhi thin jo unke samney padh kar sunai gaee thin. un likhi hui hadison ke zakheere mein Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ki ye hadis bhi thi ke abu-Talha aur Anas-bin-Nazar ne Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ko dagh laga kar unka ilaaj kya tha ya abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ne unko khud apne hath se daaghaa tha aur Ibaad-bin-Mansoor ne bayan kya, unse Ayub ne, unse abu-Qilaba ne aur unse Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne qabila Ansar ke kuchh gharaanon ko zahreeley janwaron ke kaatney aur kaan ki takleef mein jhadney ki ijazat di thi to Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke zaatul-janb ki bimari mein mujhey daaghaa gaya tha Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki zindagi main aur us waqt abu-Talha, Anas-bin-Nazar aur Zaid-bin-Saabit (Raziallahu anhu) maujood they aur abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ne mujhey daaghaa thaa."
5722,jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sar par (Uhud ke din) khud toot gaya aap ka Mubarak chehra khoon aalud ho gaya aur samney ke daant toot gaey to Ali (Raziallahu anhu) dhaal bhar-bhar kar pani latey they aur Fatima (Raziallahu anha) aap ke chehra Mubarak se khoon dho rahi thin. phir jab Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ne dekha ke khoon pani se bhi zyada aa raha hai to unhon-ne aik boriyaa jalaa kar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zakhmon par lagaya aur us se khoon ruka .
5723,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''bukhaar jahannam ki bhap mein se hai to uski garmi ko pani se bujhaao.'' Naafe ne bayan kya ke Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) (ko jab bukhar aata to) yun dua kartey ke ''Allah ! ham se us azab ko door kar de.''
5724,Asma binte-abii-bakar siddeeq (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan jab koi bukhar mein mubtala aurat laai jati thi to wo uske liye dua kartin aur uske garebaan mein pani daaltiin wo bayan karti thin ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein hukm diya tha ke bukhar ko pani se thanda karein.
5725,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''bukhaar jahannam ki bhap mein se hai isliye usey pani se thanda karo.''
5726,"maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''bukhaar jahannam ki bhap mein se hai, to usey pani se thanda kar liya karo."
5727,"qabila ukul aur Uraina ke kuchh log Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur Islam ke barey mein guftgu ki. unhon-ne kaha ke aey Allah ke Nabi ! ham maweshii waley hain ham log ahale-Madeena ki tarah kisaan nahi hain. Madina ki aab w hua unhein muwafiq nahi aai thi, chunanche Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unke liye chand oonton aur aik charwaahey ka hukm diya aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke wo log un oonton ke sath bahar chaley jayen aur unka doodh aur peshab piein. wo log chaley gaey lekin Harra ke nazdeek pahunch kar wo Islam se murtad ho gaey aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke charwaahey ko qatl kar daala aur oonton ko lekar bhag padey jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko uski khabar mili to aap ne unki talash mein aadmi daudaaey phir aap ne unke mutaalliq hukm diya aur unki aankhon mein salaaii pher di gaee, unke hath kaat diye gaey aur Harra ke kinarey unhein chhod diya gaya, wo usi haalat mein mar gaey."
5728,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jab tum sun lo ke kisi jagah taaoon ki wabaa phail rahi hai to wahan mat jao lekin jab kisi jagah ye wabaa phoot padey aur tum wahin maujood ho to us jagah se niklo bhi mat. (habeeb bin abi Sabit ne bayan kya ke maine Ibrahim bin Sad se) kaha tum ne khud ye hadis Usama (Raziallahu anhu) se suni hai ke unhon-ne Sad (Raziallahu anhu) se bayan kya aur unhon-ne iska inkar nahi kya? farmaya ke haan.
5729,"umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) Sham (Syria) tashrif ley ja rahe they jab aap maqam sargh par pahunchey to aap ki mulaqat faujon ke ameeron abu-Ubaida-bin-Jarraah (Raziallahu anhu) aur aap ke sathiyon se hui. un logon ne ameerul-momineen ko bataya ke taaoon ki wabaa Sham (Syria) mein phoot padi hai. Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke is par umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke mere paas muhaajireene-awwaleen ko bula laao. aap unhein bula laey to umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne unse mashwara kya aur unhein bataya ke Sham (Syria) mein taaoon ki wabaa phoot padi hai, muhajireen awwaleen ki raayein mukhtalif ho gaiin. kuchh logon ne kaha ke sahaba Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sathiyon ki baqi bachi jamat aap ke sath hai aur ye munasib nahi hai ke aap unhein us wabaa mein daal dein. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke achchha ab aap log tashrif ley jayen phir farmaya ke Ansar ko bulao . main Ansar ko bula kar laya aap ne unse bhi mashwara kya aur unhon-ne bhi muhajireen ki tarah ikhtilaf kya koi kehney laga chalo, koi kehney laga lot jao. ameerul-momineen ne farmaya ke ab aap log bhi tashrif ley jayen phir farmaya ke haan, par jo Quraish ke badey boodhey hain jo fateh Makka ke waqt Islam qabool karke Madina aaey they unhein bula laao, main unhein bula kar laya. un logon mein koi ikhtilaf raey paida nahi hua sab ne kaha ke hamara khayal hai ke aap logon ko sath lekar wapas lot chalein aur wabaaii mulk mein logon ko na lekar jaaein. ye suntey hi umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne logon mein elaan kara diya ke main subah ko oont par Sawar ho kar wapas Madina Munawra lot jaaunga tum log bhi wapas chalo. subah ko aisa hi hua abu-Ubaida ibne- Jarrah (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha kya Allah ki taqdeer se faraar ikhtiyar kya jaeyga umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : kash! ye baat kisi aur ne kahi hoti haan ham Allah ki taqdeer se faraar ikhtiyar kar rahe hain lekin Allah hi ki taqdeer ki taraf. kya tumharey paas oont hun aur tum unhein lekar kisi aisi wadi mein jao jiske 2 kinarey hon aik sar-sabz shaadaab aur doosra khushk. kya ye waqia nahi ke agar tum sar-sabz kinarey par charaaogey to wo bhi Allah ki taqdeer se hoga aur khushk kinarey par charaaogey to wo bhi Allah ki taqdeer se hi hoga. bayan kya ke phir Abdur-Rehman-bin-Auf (Raziallahu anhu) aagey wo apni kisi zarurat ki wjah se us waqt maujood nahi they unhon-ne bataya ke mere paas masla se mutaalliq aik ilm hai. maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna hai Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jab tum kisi sar zameen main (wabaa ke mutaalliq) suno to wahan na jao aur jab aisi jagah wabaa aa jaey jahan tum khud maujood ho to wahan se mat niklo. rawi ne bayan kya ke is par umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne Allah Taala ki hamd ki aur phir wapas ho gaey."
5730,"umr (Raziallahu anhu) Sham (Syria) ke liye rawaana huey jab maqam Sargh mein pahunchey to aapko khabar mili ke Sham (Syria) mein taaoon ki wabaa phoot padi hai. phir Abdur-Rehman-bin-Auf (Raziallahu anhu) ne unko khabar di ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jab tum wabaa ke mutaalliq suno ke wo kisi jagah hai to wahan na jao aur jab kisi aisi jagah wabaa phoot padey jahan tum maujood ho to wahan se bhi mat bhaago (wabaa mein taaoon, haiza wghaira sab dakhil hain)."
5731,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' Madina Munawra mein dajjal dakhil nahi ho sakega aur na taaoon aa sakega.''
5732,"Yahya bin Sirin ka kis bimari mein intiqal hua tha. maine kaha ke taaoon mein, bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke taaoon har musalman ke liye shahadat hai."
5733,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke pet ki bimari mein yani haize se marney wala Shahid hai aur taaoon ki bimari mein marney wala Shahid hai.
5734,aap ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se taaoon ke mutaalliq poochha. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ye aik azab tha Allah Taala jis par chahta is par usko bhejta tha phir Allah Taala ne usey momineen (ummat muhammadiya ke liye) rehmat bana diya ab koi bhi Allah ka banda agar sabr ke sath us Shahar mein thehra rahe jahan taaoon phoot padaa ho aur yaqin rakhta hai ke jo kuchh Allah Taala ne uske liye likh diya hai uske siwa usko aur koi nuqsan nahi pahunch sakta aur phir taaoon mein iska intiqal ho jaey to usey Shahid jaisa sawab milega. Hibban bin halal ke sath us hadis ko Nazar-bin-Shumail ne bhi Dawud se riwayat kya hai.
5735,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apne maut ke marz main apne uper muawwizaat ( sura Ikhlas , sura Falaq aur sura Naas (ka dam kya kartey they. phir jab aap ke liye dushwar ho gaya to main unka dam aap par kya karti thi aur barkat ke liye Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka hath aap ke jism Mubarak par bhi pher leti thi. phir maine iske mutaalliq puchha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kis tarah dam kartey they, unhon-ne bataya ke apne hath par dam karke hath ko chehrey par phera kartey they."
5736,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke chand sahaba dar-haalate-safar Arab ke aik qabeele par guzrey. qabeele walon ne unki ziyaafat nahi ki kuchh der baad us qabeele ke sardaar ko bichhu ne kaat liya, ab qabeele walon ne un sahaba se kaha ke aap logon ke paas koi dawaa ya koi jhadney wala hai. sahaba ne kaha ke tum logon ne hamein mehman nahi banaya aur ab ham us waqt tak dam nahi karengey jab tak tum hamarey liye uski mazdoorii na muqarrar kar do. chunanche un logon ne chand bakriyan deeni manzoor kar lin phir (abu-Saeed Khudri (rz)) sura Fatiha padhney lagey aur is par dam karne mein munh ka thook bhi us jagah par dalney lagey. us se wo shakhs achchha ho gaya. chunanche qabeele waley bakriyan lekar aaey lekin sahaba ne kaha ke jab tak ham Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se na poochh lein ye bakriyan nahi ley saktey phir jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se puchha to aap muskuraaey aur farmaya tumhen kaisey malum ho gaya tha ke sura Fatiha se dam bhi kya ja sakta hai, un bakriyon ko ley lo aur is mein mera bhi hissey lagaao."
5737,"chand sahaba aik pani se guzrey jiske paas ke qabeele mein bichho ka kaataa hua aik shakhs tha. qabeele ka aik shakhs unke paas aaya aur kaha kya aap logon mein koi dam jhaad karne wala hai. hamarey qabeele mein aik shakhs ko bichhu ne kaat liya hai chunanche sahaba ki us jamat mein se aik sahabi us shakhs ke sath gaey aur chand bakriyon ki shart ke sath us shakhs par sura Fatiha padhi, us se wo achchha ho gaya wo sahib shart ke mutabiq bakriyan apne sathiyon ke paas laey to unhon-ne usey qabool kar lena pasand nahi kya aur kaha ke Allah ki kitab par tum ne ujrat ley li. aakhir jab sab log Madina aaey to arz kya ke ya Rasulullah! un sahib ne Allah ki kitab par ujrat ley li hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jin chizon par tum ujrat ley saktey ho unmein se zyada uski mustahiq Allah ki kitab hi hai."
5738,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey hukm diya ya (aap ne is tarah bayan kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne) hukm diya ke nazare-bad lag janey par muawwizatain se dam kar liya jaey.
5739,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unke ghar mein aik ladki dekhi jiske chehrey par (nazare-bad lagney ki wjah se) kaley dhabbey pad gaey they. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke is par dam kara do kyonke usey nazare-bd lag gaee hai. aur Aqeel ne kaha unse Zohri ne, unhein Urwa ne khabar di aur unhon-ne usey Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se mursalan riwayat kya hai. Muhammad-bin-harab ke sath us hadis ko Abdullaah-bin-Saalim ne bhi Zubaidi se riwayat kya hai."
5740,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke nazare-bad lagna haq hai aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jism par godney se mana farmaayaa.
5741,maine Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se zahreeley janwar ke kaatney mein jhadney ke mutaalliq puchha to unhon-ne kaha ke har zahreeley janwar ke kaatney mein jhadney ki Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ijazat di hai.
5742,"main aur Sabit Bunani Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein hazir huey. Sabit ne kaha : abu-Hamza! (Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ki kunniyat) meri tabeeat kharaab ho gaee hai. Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha phir kyon na main tum par wo dua padh kar dam kar dun jisey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) padha kartey they, Sabit ne kaha ke zaroor keejiye. Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne is par ye dua padh kar dam kya اللهم رب Naas مذهب الباس اشف أنت الشافي لا شافي إلا أنت ، Mina padhi. شفاء لا يغادر سقما''aey Allah ! logon ke rab! takleef ko door kar dene waley ! shifa ata farma, to hi shifa dene wala hai terey siwa koi shifa dene wala nahi, aisi shifa ata farma ke bimari bilkul baqi na rahe."
5743,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apne ghar ke kuchh ( beemaaron ( par ye dua padh kar dam kartey aur apna daahinaa hath phertey aur ye dua padhtey اللهم رب Naas أذهب الباس ، Mina padhi. اشفه وأنت الشافي ، Mina padhi. لا شفاء إلا شفاؤك ، Mina padhi. شفاء لا يغادر سقما ''aey Allaah! logon ke paalne waale! takleef ko door kar de, usey shifa dedey to hi shifa dene wala hai. teri shifa ke siwa koi shifa nahi, aisi shifa ( de) ke kisi qism ki bimari baqi na reh jaaey.'' Sufiyan Sory ne bayan kya ke maine ye dua Mansoor bin Motamir ke samney bayan ki to unhon-ne mujh se ye Ibrahim Nakhai se bayan ki, unse Masruq ne aur unse Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne isi tarah bayan ki."
5744,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) dam kya kartey they aur ye dua padhtey they امسح الباس رب Naas ، Mina ‏‏‏‏بيدك الشفاء ، Mina ‏‏‏‏لا كاشف له إلا أنت‏ ''takleef ko door kar de, aey logon ke paalanhaar! terey hi hath mein shifa hai, terey siwa takleef ko door karne wala koi aur nahi hai.''"
5745,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mareez ke liye (kalimey ki ungli zameen par laga kar) ye dua padhtey they ( بسم الله , Mina تربة أرضنا‏ . Mina بريقة بعضنا , Mina ‏‏‏‏يشفى سقيمنا بإذن ربنا‏) ''Allaah ke naam ki madad se hamari zameen ki mitti ham mein se kisi ke thook ke sath taake hamara mareez shifa paaey hamarey rab ke hukm se.''"
5746,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) dam kartey waqt ye dua padha kartey they ( تربة أرضنا , Mina وريقة بعضنا , Mina ‏‏‏‏يشفى سقيمنا , Mina بإذن ربنا‏ Mina .) '' hamari zameen ki mitti aur hamara kuchh thook hamarey rab ke hukm se hamarey mareez ko shifa ho. ''"
5747,"maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke beshak achchha khuwab Allah ki taraf se hota hai, aur hilm (buraa khuwab jis mein ghabraahat ho) shaitan ki taraf se hota hai is liye jab tum mein se koi shakhs koi aisa khuwab dekhey jo bura ho to jaagtey hi teen martaba baain taraf thoo-thoo karey aur us khuwab ki burai se Allah ki panah maangey, is tarah khuwab ka usey nuqsan nahi hoga aur abu-Salma ne kaha ke pahley kuchh khuwab mujh par pahaad se bhi zyada bhari hota tha jab se maine ye hadis suni aur is par amal karne laga, ab mujhey koi parwah nahi hoti."
5748,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab apne bistar par aaraam farmaney ke liye let'tey to apni donon hatheliyon par) قل هو الله أحد (aur ( قل أعوذ برب Naas (aur ( قل أعوذ برب Falaq ( sab padh kar dam kartey phir donon hathon ko apne chehra par aur jism ke jis hissey tak hath pahunch paata phertey. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha ke phir jab aap bimar hotey to aap mujhey isi tarah karne ka hukm detey they. Yunus ne bayan kya ke maine ibne-Shahab ko bhi dekha ke wo jab apne bistar par let'tey isi tarah unko padh kar dam kya kartey they.
5749,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke chand sahaba ( 300 log ( aik safar ke liye rawaana huey jisey unhein tay karna tha rastey mein unhon-ne Arab ke aik qabeele mein padao kya aur chaha ke qabeele waley unki mehmani karein lekin unhon-ne inkar kya, phir us qabeele ke sardaar ko bichho ne kaat liya usey achchha karne ki har tarah ki koshish unhon-ne kar dali lekin kisi se kuchh fayda nahi hua. aakhir unhiin mein se kisi ne kaha ke ye log jinhoney tumharey qabeele mein padao kar rakha hai unke paas bhi chalo, mumkin hai unmein se kisi ke paas koi mantar ho. chunanche wo sahaba ke paas aaey aur kaha logo! hamarey sardaar ko bichho ne kaat liya hai ham ne har tarah ki bahut koshish uske liye kar dali lekin kisi se koi fayda nahi hua kya tum logon mein se kisi ke paas uske liye mantr hai? sahaba mein se aik sahib ( Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu)) ne kaha ke haan, Allah ki qism mein jhaadanaa janta hun lekin ham ne tum se kaha tha ke hamari mehmani karo) ham musaafir hain) to tum ne inkar kar diya tha isliye main bhi us waqt tak nahi jhaadunga jab tak tum mere liye uski mazdoorii na thehra do. chunanche un logon ne kuchh bakriyon ( 30 ( par mamla kar liya. ab ye sahabi rawaana huey. ye zameen par thooktey jatey aur) الحمد لله رب العالمين ( Mina padhtey jatey uski barkat se wo aisa ho gaya jaisey uski rassii khul gaee ho aur wo is tarah chalney laga jaisey usey koi takleef hi na rahi ho. bayan kya ke phir wada ke mutabiq qabila walon ne un sahabi ki mazdoorii ( 30 bakriyan ( ada kar di kuchh logon ne kaha ke unko taqseem kar lo lekin jinhoney jhaada tha unhon-ne kaha ke abhi nahi, pahley ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hun poori sura haal aap ke samney bayan kar dein phir dekhein Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hamein kya hukm farmatey hain. chunanche sab log Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey to aap se iska zikr kya Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tumhen kaisey malum ho gaya tha ke is se dam kya ja sakta hai? tum ne achchha kya jao unko taqseem kar lo aur mera bhi apne sath aik hissey lagaao ."
5750,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (apne ghar ke) kuchh logon par dam kartey waqt apna daahinaa hath phertey (aur ye dua padhtey they) أذهب الباس رب Naas ، Mina ‏‏‏‏واشف أنت الشافي ، Mina ‏‏‏‏لا شفاء إلا شفاؤك ، Mina ‏‏‏‏شفاء لا يغادر سقما ''takleef ko door kar de aey logon ke rab! aur shifa de, to hi shifa dene wala hai, shifa wahi hai jo teri taraf se ho aisi shifa ke bimari zara bhi baqi na reh jaaey.'' ( Sufiyan ne kaha ke) phir maine ye Mansoor se bayan kya to unhon-ne mujh se Ibrahim Nakhai se bayan kya, unse Masruq ne aur unse Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne us hi ki tarah bayan kya."
5751,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apne wafat k marz mein muawwizaat padh kar phoonktey they phir jab aap ke liye ye dushwar ho gaya to main aap par dam kya karti thi aur barkat ke liye Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka hath aap ke jism par pherti thi. ( Mamar ne bayan kya ke) phir maine ibne-Shahab se sawal kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kis tarah dam kya kartey they? unhon-ne bayan kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) pahley apne donon hathon par phoonk maartey phir unko chehrey par pher letey.
5752,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik din hamarey paas bahar tashrif laey aur farmaya ke (khuwaab mein) mujh par tamam ummatein pesh ki gaiin. kuchh Nabi guzartey aur unke sath (unki ittaba (pairvi) karne wala) sirf aik hota. kuchh guzartey aur unke sath 2 hotey kuchh ke sath poori jamat hoti aur kuchh ke sath koi bhi na hota phir maine aik badi jamat dekhi jis se aasman ka kinara dhak gaya tha mein samjha ke ye meri hi ummat hogi lekin mujh se kaha gaya ke ye Musa (Alaihissalam) aur unki ummat ke log hain phir mujh se kaha ke dekho maine aik bahut badi jamat dekhi jisne aasmanon ka kinara dhanp liya hai. phir mujh se kaha gaya ke idhar dekho, idhar dekho, maine dekha ke bahut si jamatein hain jo tamam ufuq par muheet thin. kaha gaya ke ye aap ke ummat hai aur is mein se 70 hazaar wo log hongey jo be-hisaab jannat mein dakhil kiye jaeinge phir sahaba mukhtalif jaghon mein uth kar chaley gaey aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne uski wazaahat nahi ki ke ye 70 hazaar kon log hongey. sahaba kiram (Raziallahu anhu) ne aapas mein iske mutaalliq muzaakre kya aur kaha ke hamari paidaaish to shirk mein hui thi albatta baad mein ham Allah aur uske rasool par eman ley aaey lekin ye 70 hazaar hamarey betey hongey jo paidaaish hi se musalman hain. jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye baat pahunchi to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ye 70 hazaar wo log hongey jo badfaalii nahi kartey, na mantr se jhaad-phoonk karatey hain aur na dagh lagaatey hain balke apne rab par bharosa kartey hain. ye sun kar Ukaasha-bin-Mohsin (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! kya main bhi unmein se hon? farmaya ke haan. aik doosrey sahib Sad-bin-Ubada (Raziallahu anhu) ne khadey ho kar arz kya main bhi unmein se hoon? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Ukasha tum se bazi le gaey ke tum se pahley Ukasha ke liye jo hona tha ho chukaa."
5753,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''beemaarii mein chhoot-chhaat ki aur badshigoonii ki koi asl nahi aur agar nahoosat hoti to ye sirf teen chizon mein hoti aurat mein, ghar main aur ghodey mein.''"
5754,"maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''badshigoonii ki koi asl nahi albatta nek faal lena kuchh bura nahi hai.''sahaaba kiram (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya : nek faal kya cheez hai? farmaya ''koii aisi baat sunnaa.''"
5755,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''badshigoonii ki koi asl nahi aur is mein behtar faal nek hai.'' logon ne puchha ke nek faal kya hai ya rasoolullaah? farmaya ''nek baat jo tum mein se koi suney.''
5756,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''chhoot lag janey ki koi asl nahi aur na badshigoonii ki koi asl hai aur mujhey achi faal pasand hai.'' yani koi kalima khair aur nek baat jo kisi ke munh se suni jaey (jaisaa ke uper bayan hua).
5757,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' chhoot lag jana badshigoonii ya ullu ya safar ki nahoosat ye koi cheez nahi hai.''
5758,qabila huzail ki 2 aurton ke barey mein jinhoney jhagdaa kya tha yahan tak ke unmein se aik aurat ne dusri ko patthar phenk kar maara (jiska naam Muleka binte- Uwemir tha) wo patthar aurat ke pet mein ja kar laga. ye aurat haamla thi isliye iske pet ka bachcha (patthar ki chot se) mar gaya. ye mamla donon fareeq Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas le gaey to aap ne faisla kya ke aurat ke pet ke bachcha ki diyat aik ghulam ya baandi aazad karna hai jis aurat par taawaan wajib hua tha uske wali (hamal bin Malik bin naabgha ( ne kaha ya Rasulullah! main aisi cheez ki diyat kaisey de dun jisne na khaya na piyaa na bola aur na wilaadat ke waqt uski awaz hi sunai dii? aisi sura main to kuchh bhi diyat nahi ho sakti . Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is par farmaya ke ye shakhs to kaahinon ka bhai malum hota hai.
5759,"2 auratein thin, aik ne dusri ko patthar de maara jis se uske pet ka hamal gir gaya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us maamle mein aik ghulam ya baandi ka diyat mein diye janey ka faisla kya."
5760,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne janeen jisey uski maa ke pet mein mar daala gaya ho, ki diyat ke taur par aik ghulam ya aik baandi diye janey ka faisla kya tha jisey diyat deeni thi usne kaha ke aisey bachche ki diyat aakhir kyon dun jisne na khaayaa, na piyaa, na bola aur na wilaadat ke waqt hi awaz nikaalii? aisi sura main to diyat nahi ho saktii. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ye shakhs to kaahinon ka bhai malum hota hai."
5761,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kuttey ki qeemat , zina ki ujrat aur kaahin ki kahaanat ki wjah se milney waley hadiya se mana farmaya hai."
5762,kuchh logon ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kaahinon ke mutaalliq puchha Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke uski koi buniyad nahi. logon ne kaha ke ya Rasulullah ! kabhi-kabhi wo hamein aisi cheezein bhi bataatey hain jo sahi ho jati hain. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ye kalima haq hota hai. usey kaahin kisi jinnii se sun leta hai wo jinnii apne dost kaahin ke kaan mein daal jata hai aur phir ye kaahin iske sath so jhoot mila kar bayan kartey hain. Ali-bin-Abdullaah madeenii ne bayan kya ke Abdur-Razzaq us kalima ( تلك الكلمة من الحق ( ko mursalan riwayat kartey they phir unhon-ne kaha mujh ko ye khabar pahunchi ke Abdur-Razzaq iske baad usko musnadan Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat kya hai.
5763,"bani zuraiq ke aik shakhs Yahudi Labid bin Aa'sam ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par jaadoo kar diya tha aur uski wjah se Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kisi cheez ke mutaalliq khayal kartey ke aap ne wo kaam kar liya hai halanke aap ne wo kaam na kya hota. aik din ya ( rawi ne bayan kya ke) aik raat Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mere yahan tashrif rakhtey they aur musalsal dua kar rahe they phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Aaisha ! tumhen malum hai Allah se jo baat mein poochh raha tha, us ne iska jawab mujhey de diya. mere paas 2 ( Farishtey Jibraeel w Mikaail (Alaihissalam) ( aaey. aik mere sar ki taraf khada ho gaya aur doosra mere paon ki taraf . aik ne apne doosrey sathi se puchha un sahib ki bimari kya hai? doosrey ne kaha ke un par jaadoo hua hai. us ne puchha kis ne jaadoo kya hai? jawab diya ke Labid ne. puchha kis cheez mein ? jawab diya ke kanghey aur sar ke baal mein jo nar khajoor ke khoshey mein rakhey huey hain. sawal kya aur ye jaadoo hai kahan ? jawab diya ke zarwaan ke kuwein mein. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us kuwein par apne chand sahaba ke sath tashrif le gaey aur jab wapas aaey to farmaya Aaisha ! iska pani aisa ( surkh ( tha jaisey mahndii ka nichod hota hai aur uske khajoor ke darakhton ke sar ( uper ka hissa ( shaitan ke saron ki tarah they maine arz kya ya Rasulullah ! aap ne us jaadoo ko bahar kyon nahi kar diya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Allah Taala ne mujhey us se aafiyat de di isliye maine munasib nahi samjha ke ab main khah-m-khah logon mein us burai ko phailaaun phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us jaadoo ka saman kanghi baal khurmaa ka ghilaaf hotey hain usi mein dafn kara diya. Esa-bin-Yonus ke sath us hadis ko abu-Usama aur abu-Zamra (Anas bin ayaaz) aur ibne-abi zinaad teenon ne Hisham se yun riwayat kya aur Lais bin Miswar aur Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne Hisham se yun riwayat kya hai) في مشط ومشاقة‏ . Mina , المشاطة ( usey kehtey hain jo baal kanghi karne mein niklin sar ya dadhi ke aur) مشاقة‏) rooii ke taar yani soot ke taar ko kehtey hain."
5764,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''tabaah kar dene wali cheez Allah ke sath shirk karna hai us se bacho aur jaadoo karne karaaney se bhi bacho.''
5765,"mujh se ye hadis aale-Urwa ne Urwa se bayan ki, isliye maine (Urwa ke betey) Hisham se iske barey mein puchha to unhon-ne ham se apne walid ( Urwa ( se bayan kya ke unse Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par jaadoo kar diya gaya tha aur iska aap par ye asar hua tha aapko khayal hota ke aap ne paak beeviyon mein se kisi ke sath ham-bistarii ki hai halanke aap ne ki nahi hoti. Sufiyan Sory ne bayan kya ke jaadoo ki ye sabse sakht qism hai jab iska ye asar ho phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya Aaisha! tumhen malum hai Allah Taala se jo baat maine poochhi thi iska jawab us ne Kab ka de diya hai. mere paas 2 Farishtey aaey aik mere sar ke paas khada ho gaya aur doosra mere paon ke paas. jo farishta mere sar ki taraf khada tha us ne doosrey se kaha un sahib ka kya haal hai? doosrey ne jawab diya ke un par jaadoo kar diya gaya hai. puchha ke kis ne un par jaadoo kya hai? jawab diya ke Labid ne ye yahudiyon ke haleef bani zuraiq ka aik shakhs tha aur munafiq tha. sawal kya ke kis cheez mein un par jaadoo kya hai? jawab diya ke kanghey aur baal mein. puchha jaadoo hai kahaan? jawab diya ke nar khajoor ke khoshey mein jo zarwaan ke kuwein ke andar rakhey huey patthar ke nichey dafn hai. bayan kya ke phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us kuwein par tashrif le gaey aur jaadoo andar se nikaalaa. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke yahi wo kunwaan hai jo mujhey khuwab mein dikhaya gaya tha iska pani mahndii ke arq jaisa rangeen tha aur uske khajoor ke darakhton ke sar shaitanon ke saron jaisey they. bayan kya ke phir wo jaadoo kuwein mein se nikala gaya. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke maine kaha aap ne us jaadoo ka tod kyon nahi karaya. farmaya : haan Allah Taala ne mujhey shifa di ab main logon mein aik shor hona pasand nahi karta."
5766,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par jaadoo kar diya gaya tha aur iska asar ye tha ke aapko khayal hota ke aap koi cheez kar chukey hain halanke wo cheez na ki hoti aik din Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mere yahan tashrif rakhtey they aur musalsal duaein kar rahe they, phir farmaya : Aaisha ! tumhen malum hai Allah Taala se jo baat maine poochhi thi iska jawab usne mujhey de diya hai. maine kaha wo kya baat hai ya Rasulullah ! Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya mere paas 2 Farishtey ( Jibraeel w Mikaail (Alaihissalam) ( aaey aur aik mere sar ke paas khada ho gaya aur doosra paon ki taraf phir aik ne apne doosrey sathi se kaha un sahib ki takleef kya hai? doosrey ne jawab diya ke in par jaadoo kya gaya hai. puchha kis ne un par jaadoo kya hai? farmaya bani zuraiq ke Labid bin Aa'sam Yahudi ne, puchha kis cheez mein? jawab diya ke kanghey aur baal mein jo nar khajoor ke khoshey mein rakha hua hai. puchha aur wo jaadoo rakha kahan hai? jawab diya ke doran ke kuwein mein. bayan kya ke phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apne chand sahaba ke sath us kuwein par tashrif le gaey aur usey dekha wahan khajoor ke darakht bhi they phir aap wapas Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke yahan tashrif laey aur farmaya (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Allah ki qism ! iska pani mahndii ke arq jaisa ( surkh ( hai aur uske khajoor ke darakht shayatin ke saron jaisey hain. maine arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! wo kanghi baal wghaira ghilaaf se nikalwaaey ya nahi. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya nahi, sun lo Allah ne to mujh ko shifa de di, tandurust kar diya ab main dara kahin logon mein aik shor na phailey aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us saman ke gaad dene ka hukm diya wo gaad diya gaya."
5767,2 aadmi poorab ki taraf (mulk iraaq) se (9 hijri mein) Madina aaey aur logon ko khitab kya log unki taqreer se bahut mutassir huey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke kuchh taqreerein bhi jaadoo bhari hoti hain ya ye farmaya ke kuchh taqreer jaadoo hoti hain.
5768,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jo shakhs rozaana chand ajwa khajoorein kha liya karey usey us din raat tak zahar aur jaadoo nuqsan nahi pahuncha sakengey. Ali-bin-Abdullaah madeenii ke siwa doosrey rawi ne bayan kya ke saat (7) khajoorein kha liya kare.
5769,"maine Aamir-bin-Sad se suna, unhon-ne Sad-bin-abi-Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, unhon-ne bayan kya ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jis shakhs ne subah ke waqt saat (7) ajwa khajoorein kha lein us din usey na zahar nuqsan pahuncha sakta hai aur na jaadoo."
5770,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke chhoot lag jana , safar ki nahoosat aur ullu ki nahoosat koi cheez nahi. aik dehati ne kaha : ya Rasulullah ! phir us oont ke mutaalliq kya kaha jaeyga jo registaan mein hiran ki tarah saaf chamakdaar hota hai lekin khaarish wala oont usey mil jata hai aur usey bhi khaarish laga deta hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya lekin pahley oont ko kis ne khaarish lagai thi?"
5771,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke koi shakhs apne bimar oonton ko kisi ke sihat mand oonton mein na ley jaey. Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne pehli hadis ka inkar kya. ham ne ( Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se) arz kya ke aap hi ne ham se ye hadis nahi bayan ki hai ke chhoot ye nahi hota phir wo (ghussa mein) habshi zaban bolney lagey. abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehman ne bayan kya ke is hadis ke siwa maine Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ko aur koi hadis bhooltey nahi dekha.
5772,"mujhey Salim bin-Abdullah aur Hamza ne khabar di aur unse Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke chhoot lag janey ki koi haqiqat nahi hai, badshigoonii ki koi asl nahi. (agar mumkin hoti to ( nahoosat teen chizon mein hoti, ghodey mein, aurat main aur ghar mein."
5773,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke chhoot ki koi haqiqat nahi.
5774,mareez oonton wala apne oont tandurust oonton waley ke oont mein na chhodey .
5775,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke chhoot koi cheez nahi hai. is par aik dehati ne khadey ho kar puchha aap ne dekha hoga ke aik oont registaan mein hiran jaisa saaf rehta hai lekin jab wahi aik khaarish waley oont ke paas aa jata hai to usey bhi khaarish ho jati hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya lekin pahley oont ko kis ne khaarish lagai thi.
5776,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke chhoot lagna koi cheez nahi hai aur badshigoonii nahi hai albatta nek faal mujhey pasand hai. sahabi ne arz kya nek faal kya hai? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke achi baat munh se nikaalnaa ya kisi se sun lenaa.
5777,"jab khaibar fateh hua to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko aik bakri hadiye mein pesh ki gaee (eik Yahudi aurat Zenab binte- hars ne pesh ki thi) jis mein zahar bharaa hua tha, is par Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke haan, par jitney Yahudi hain unhein mere paas jama karo. chunanche sab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas jama kiye gaey. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke main tum se aik baat poochhunga kya tum mujhey sahi saheeh baat bata doge? unhon-ne kaha ke haan, aey abul-Qaasim! phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tumhara pardada kon hai? unhon-ne kaha ke fulaan. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tum jhoot kehtey ho tumhara pardada to falan hai. is par wo boley ke aap ne sach farmaya, durust farmaya, phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse farmaya kya agar main tum se koi baat poochhunga to tum mujhey sach sach bata doge ? unhon-ne kaha ke haan, aey abul-Qaasim ! aur agar ham jhoot bolein bhi to aap hamara jhoot pakad lengey jaisa ke abhi hamarey pardada ke mutaalliq aap ne hamara jhoot pakad liya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke dozakh waley kon log hain? unhon-ne kaha ke kuchh din ke liye to ham usmein rahengey phir aap log hamari jagah ley lengey. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tum usmein zillat ke sath padey rahogey, Allah ki qasam! ham usmein tumhari jagah kabhi nahi lengey. aap ne phir unse malum farmaya kya agar main tum se aik baat poochhoon to tum mujhey iske mutaalliq sahi saheeh bata doge? unhon-ne kaha ke haan? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya kya tum ne us bakri mein zahar milaya tha, unhon-ne kaha ke haan. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya ke tumhen us kaam par kis jazbey ne aamada kya tha? unhon-ne kaha ke hamara maqsad ye tha ke agar aap jhootey hongey to hamein aap se nijat mil jaeygi aur agar sachey hongey to aapko nuqsan nahi pahuncha sakega."
5778,"maine Zakwan se suna, wo Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se ye hadis bayan kartey they ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jisne pahaad se apne aapko gira kar khudkushii kar li wo jahannam ki aag mein hoga aur is mein hamesha padaa rahega aur jisne zahar pi kar khudkushii kar li wo zahar iske sath mein hoga aur jahannam ki aag mein wo usey isi tarah hamesha peetaa rahega aur jisne lohey ke kisi hathiyar se khudkushii kar li to uska hathiyar uske sath mein hoga aur jahannam ki aag mein hamesha ke liye wo usey apne pet mein maarta rahega."
5779,"maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''jo shakhs subah ke waqt saat (7) ajwa khajoorein kha ley usey us din zahar nuqsan pahuncha sakega aur na jaadoo.''"
5780,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne har daant se khaney waley darinde janwar (ke gosht) se mana farmaya, Zohri ne bayan kya ke maine ye hadis us waqt tak nahi suni jab tak Sham (Syria) nahi aaya."
5781,maine abu-Idrees se puchha kya ham ( dawaa ke taur par) gadhi ke doodh se wuzu kar saktey hain ya usey pi saktey hain ya darinda janwaron ke pittey istemal kar saktey hain ya oont ka peshab pi saktey hain. abu-Idrees ne kaha ke musalman oont ke peshab ko dawaa ke taur par istemal kartey they aur is mein koi harj nahi samajhtey they. albatta gadhi ke doodh ke barey mein hamein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki ye hadis pahunchi hai ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne iske gosht se mana farmaya tha. iske doodh ke mutaalliq hamein koi hukm ya manaahii Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se malum nahi hai. albatta darindon ke pittey ke mutaalliq jo ibne-Shahab ne bayan kya ke mujhey abu-Idrees Kholani ne khabar di aur unhein abu-So'lba Khushni (Raziallahu anhu) ne khabar di ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne har daant waley shikaarii darindey ka gosht khaney se mana farmaya hai.
5782,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' jab makkhii tum mein se kisi ke bartan mein pad jaey to poori makkhii ko bartan mein dubo de aur phir usey nikal kar phenk de kyonke iske aik par main shifa aur doosrey mein bimari hai.''
